Test Case1
Title: Authorization.

1 Open site "https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/"
2 Enter login "qaauto" in the field "Username".
3 Enter password "123456qwerty" in the field "Password".
4 Click on the button "Sign in".

Expected result: The user goes to the home page of the site.
---------------------------------------------------
Test Case2
Title: Create Post.

1 On the home page of the website click on the link "Create Post".
2 Click on the button "Save New Post".
Expected result: The post cannot be created, the user is prompted to fill in the field "Title".
3 Fill in the field "Title" using only a space.
4 Click on the button "Save New Post".
Expected result: The post cannot be created, the user sees the inscription "You must provide a title.".
5 Fill in the field "Title".
6 Click on the button "Save New Post".
Expected result: The post cannot be created, the user is prompted to fill in the field "Body Content".
7 Fill in the field "Body Content" using only a space.
Expected result: The post cannot be created, the user sees the inscription "You must provide a content.".
8 Fill in the field "Body Content".
Expected result: The post was created and user sees the inscription "New post successfully created.".

----------------------------------------------------
Test Case3
Title: My Profile.

1 On the home page of the website click on the link "My Profile".

Expected result: User sees all his created posts and can edit or delete them.

------------------------------------------------------
Test Case4
Title: Link "Search".

1 On the home page of the website click on the link "Search".

Expected result: The user goes to the search menu and can enter parameters in the search bar.

-------------------------------------------------------
Test Case5
Title: Log in

1 On the home page of the website click on the button "Sign Out".

Expected result: The user is logged out and goes to the login/registration page.
